  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nAs per the work @rawfalafel is doing in #322, we have discussed having every service run a single, main routine instead of multiple different ones that have shared state. This will allow for the prevention of race conditions at runtime that will be pesky to catch and allow for simpler services.\r\n",
